In Part 1:

Application Scientist, Dr. Matúš Krajňák, will showcase how you can capture beam-sensitive materials and the dynamics of FeGe skyrmions with high-resolution and 4D scanning TEM (STEM) with superior precision.

What you will learn:

- The difference between event-based and frame-based detection and when to use each.
- How the Merlin T4 supports ultra-fast, high-resolution electron microscopy workflows.
- Real-world use cases and scientific datasets enabled by the detector.
